    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Good, well-kept car that presents nicely and should make a solid buy for someone looking for a clean driver rather than a flawless showpiece. The exterior and interior are in respectable condition overall, with the kind of light cosmetic wear, minor blemishes, and normal-use signs you\u2019d expect on an honestly represented used car. It runs and drives well, shows consistent care, and offers a strong balance between condition and value. Buyers can expect a car that looks good, feels well maintained, and is ready to enjoy, while still having a few typical imperfections if you look closely.",
