      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for anyone seeking straightforward transportation without a premium price tag. It presents as an honest used car with plenty of potential for a budget-conscious driver, commuter, or hands-on buyer looking for a practical project. A smart opportunity to secure a low-cost vehicle at an attractive price.",
