    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s a great fit for someone who wants dependable basic transport without spending a fortune, or for a handy owner who enjoys bringing a car along. Priced fairly and presented honestly, this one could be a smart buy for the money.",
      "price": 5950.0,
