      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with good bones and plenty of upside. The powertrain pulls willingly, the chassis feels composed, and it has the kind of analog character enthusiasts appreciate. Not a showroom piece and shows its age cosmetically, but it presents as a usable car that\u2019s ready to be driven, sorted, and enjoyed. A great entry point for someone who wants an affordable platform with mechanical character instead of overpaying for polish.",
      "price": 5900.0,
