      "description": "Turn heads and spark ideas with this character-filled ride that still has plenty of story left to tell. It has the kind of presence that makes a perfect project, parts car, or budget-minded fixer for someone who sees opportunity where others see a blank canvas. With timeless style, honest patina, and undeniable personality, this is the sort of vehicle that invites a hands-on owner to bring it back into the spotlight. If you\u2019ve been looking for an affordable entry point into something with soul, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
